OL,4,Cdown innocent victim
OL,6,FA driver who used his van "as a
OL,7,Fweapon" to mow down a semi-
OL,8,Fprofessional footballer leaving him
OL,9,Fwith life-changing injuries, has been
OL,10,Fjailed.
OL,12,FFrankie Bromley, 23, targeted Conna
OL,13,FSmith, 20, and another man as they
OL,14,Fstood outside a bar in Poulton-le-
OL,15,FFylde at 12.50am on 16 February.
