OL,6,FConna was admitted to intensive care
OL,7,Fafter being dragged under the van
OL,8,Fwhere he suffered eight broken ribs, a
OL,9,Fbroken collar bone, broken sternum,
OL,10,Ftwo collapsed lungs and a broken nose,
OL,11,Fas well as deep cuts on his face and
OL,12,Felbow.
OL,14,FPreston Crown Court heard Bromley then
OL,15,Fsped away through the streets of
OL,16,FPoulton, leaving his victim serious
OL,17,Finjured on the pavement, with the Ford
OL,18,FTransit van later recovered in a car
OL,19,Fpark.
