OL,6,FIn a GoFundMe appeal following the
OL,7,Fincident, Conna's dad Jay Reynolds
OL,8,Fsaid: "Despite the challenges he
OL,9,Ffaces, we are grateful that he is
OL,10,Fstill with us."
OL,12,FConna said: "This incident has had a
OL,13,Fhuge impact on me physically. My lungs
OL,14,Fare permanently damaged as a result of
OL,15,Fthe van being driven at me.
OL,17,F"My ribs are very fragile which has
OL,18,Fmeant that I can't play football
OL,19,Fanymore in case I get knocked into."
