OL,3,CDriver used 'van as weapon' to mow
OL,4,Cdown innocent victim
OL,6,FThe court was told Bromley used the
OL,7,Fvan as a weapon as he drove towards
OL,8,Fhis target and Conna - an innocent
OL,9,Fbystander, knocking them both to the
OL,10,Fground.
OL,12,FEmergency services rushed to the scene
OL,13,Fas members of the public and door
OL,14,Fstaff helped Conna.
OL,16,FBromley, 23, has now been jailed for
OL,17,Fcausing serious injury by dangerous
OL,18,Fdriving, attempted causing serious
OL,19,Finjury by dangerous driving and
OL,20,Fdangerous driving following the
OL,21,Fincident in Breck Road.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
