OL,4,Cdown innocent victim
OL,6,FHe was sentenced to six years in
OL,7,Fprison, and banned from driving for
OL,8,Fnine years, by Judge Ian Unsworth KC,
OL,9,Fat Preston Crown Court on 13 November.
OL,11,FDC Rachael Gregory, of Blackpool CID
OL,12,Fsaid: "Bromley used the hired van as a
OL,13,Fweapon that night, which led to a
OL,14,Fyoung man, who was innocently going
OL,15,Fabout his night out, being
OL,16,Fsignificantly injured.
OL,18,F"I know that this incident caused a
OL,19,Flot of concern in the community at the
OL,20,Ftime, so it was important that we
OL,21,Fbring you such a significant update.
