OL,6,F"We asked the community for their help
OL,7,Fat the time of the incident, and we
OL,8,Fknow that various members of the
OL,9,Fpublic came forward with information
OL,10,Fand footage that ultimately helped us
OL,11,Fbring Bromley to justice. For that, I
OL,12,Fwant to make my thanks to them very
OL,13,Fclear.
OL,15,F"This has been a complex
OL,16,Finvestigation, and whilst it isn't our
OL,17,Fplace to reflect on the sentence, I do
OL,18,Fhope that the victim and his loved
OL,19,Fones will feel some sense of justice
OL,20,Fand can begin to move forward with
OL,21,Ftheir lives."
